This paper discusses the history of mobile augmented reality, which involves computer graphics, human-computer interaction, computer vision, and multimedia. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), followed by cs.GR (Computer Graphics), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.AR (Augmented Reality), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
